  "title": "Tangy Flaky French Sichuan Pepper Crumble",
  "description": "This tangy and flaky dish combines the unique flavors of France with the fiery kick of Sichuan pepper, marinated overnight for an extra depth of flavor. It's perfect as a romantic dessert or snack.",
